{
  "stem": "13483.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they say we had to live on the field rations till we got to landed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anticipation.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Expectation.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A feeling of-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what is the word I want to use-- exultation, you know excitement, I think.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't feel any fear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think none of us ever felt fear.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think that, number one, the weather was so bad, when we actually landed, I think we were relieved.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "None at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Don't know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I didn't feel anything, to be quite honest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just didn't feel anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, with a rifle and then a-- and a stinger, which were, quite obviously, damn useless.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my only recollection of the landing, that I was a co-driver to a bulldozer operator.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I sat with him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, we were living targets, really, because we were well above the, you know, ordinary level.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember going-- getting off the LST.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I do remember, which always sticks in my mind, all the soldiers dead in the water.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mainly Canadians, funnily enough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They'd just been washed ashore, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we were the second wave, as far as I remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We landed at Arromanches I think about 8:00 AM, the first landings, I think, were about 5:00 AM or 6:00 AM.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So all we saw was, at that time, just the remnants, whoever got killed from the first landing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that, I think, that stuck out in my mind.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Were you being fired on?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, from a distance.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Funny enough, well, I recollect there was a-- as you came off the LST, you could just see this patch of sand, the beach, and what looked like houses.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
